data.description: B!!  Agent Remarks!!       PRICE REDUCED! In SHERWOOD'S AUSTIN GARDENS GATED COMMUNITY!  This custom-built gem, constructed in 2011, offers a 2BR 2BA layout with an array of exquisite upgrades. Step into a world of comfort and style with a newly carpeted, luxurious master suite complete with a spacious walk-in closet that will leave you in awe. Both bathrooms feature granite countertops, adding a touch of sophistication to your daily routine.  High ceilings and crown molding grace this home, enhancing its grandeur, while beautiful hardwood floors create an ambiance of timeless elegance. Additionally, this property features thoughtful handicap features, providing accessibility for all.  Relish in the convenience of a cozy covered front and back patio. The HOA even covers lawn care and the sprinkler system, making life a breeze.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own. Schedule your showing today!
